               <msContents>
                  <summary>Text 1: ff. 1ra,1-10vb,end, and 12ra,1-rb,12: [First Epistle of John] both the beginning and the end lost; the text here begins at 1 John 3:15; Text 2: f. 12ra,1-rb,12: The end of the Epistle of James (5:16-19); Text 3: f. 12rb,4fb-12vb,end: The beginning of the Epistle of Jude (1:1-5); Text 4: ff. 11r-v; and ff. 13ra,1-23vb,end: Acts of the Apostles: (the text here begins at Acts 2:4); ff. 24ra,1-57vb,end: Acts of the Apostles; (the text here begins at Acts 1:1) unfinished; Text 5: ff. 79r,1-81vb,end; Epistle of James; unfinished
                  </summary>
              
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1v" to="87v"/>
                     <title>Catholic Epistles, Acts</title>
                     
                     <note>Content includes Acts and Epistles with multiple folios and references: 1 Peter 1:12-2:14, fol. 75r-76v; 1 John 3:2-5:15, fol. 1r-3v, 5rv, 78rv; 2 John 4-13, fol. 77rv; 3 John 1-2, fol. 77v; James 1:1-3:15, 4:10-5:20, fol. 4rv, 6r-8v, 12r, 73r-74v, 79rv; Jude 1-24, fol. 9r-10v, 12rv; Acts 1:1-26:11, fol. 11rv, 13r-72v, 80r-81v.</note>
                  </msItem>
